text: Ærest andlang hrigweges to æðelwoldes gemero.
Ðanon andlang weges innan ða dæne.
Syðan be ðan andheafdan ðæt cymð to Clife.
Andlang streames on ða dic to wudetunnincga gemero.
Ðanon on ceattan broc to micghæma gemæra.
Of ðam gemero eastaweardan æft on ceattan broc.
Ðanon on ceattan gemera to ælflede gemero.
Of ðam gemere eastaweardan æft on ceattan broc.
Ðonne upp on ðone holan cumb.
Of ðam holan wege ufeweardan on ælflede gemeran.
Be ælflede gemere æft on hricwege to Wulfmeres gemere.
Ðis is ðara X hida boc æt Cliuæ ðe æðelred cing gebocode æðelmere his þegne on ece yrfæ.
